data.description: Welcome to this spacious 3 bedroom/2 full bath home in a very convenient Wyoming location.  With easy access to amenities and highways, this home boasts a large living room, a fenced in backyard, and a newer roof.  Bring your imagination and creativity to this home as the dining room could be converted into a 4th bedroom, and the stand up attic space could become usable living space or storage. Schedule your showing today before it's too late!
